1958;;Bachelor of Hearts;;British;;Wolf Rilla;;Hardy Krüger, Sylvia Syms;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bachelor_of_Hearts;;Young German maths scholar Wolf Hauser (Hardy Krüger) arrives for a year at Cambridge on a Student exchange programme. Settling into his rooms at University College, Wolf has more than his share of trouble negotiating English customs and manners, before he finds a guide and girlfriend in the shape of beautiful blonde Ann (Sylvia Syms).